        Rage Runner is a fast paced 3D runner that will challenge your
        memory and your reflexes. Blast through miles of trench in the H-C-S
        Penetrator (the ship that did the castle run in less than 2
        parsecs!) as you avoid an onslaught of fast and furious obstacles.

        Missile, Shield, Super Brake and Super Thruster powerups will help
        lead you to "FREEEEEDOOOOMMMMMM!!1" and if youÃ‚â€™re good enough,
        emblazon your initials on the high score server.  Rage Runner also
        features a robust Level Editor that allows you to create and share
        levels with the community.

        Do you have what it takes? We have faith in you!
        Features

        Fast beautiful action
        A difficulty curve that will challenge the most devout pilots
        7 hand-crafted levels, lovingly paced to their own dubstep soundtrack
        Level editor
        High score server

        URL: http://ragerunner.hypercanestudios.com/

        If you like the game, support the developers and buy it!
